title: Return of the Bloodthirsty Police
description: After being betrayed and killed by the organization he worked at, the infamous assassin ‘Bi-Gwang’ reincarnates as ‘Kim Gyeongsoo’, a police officer. He vows to take revenge on ‘Hwaguksa’, the organization of killers that has betrayed him. 킬러경찰, killer Police, Killer Cop
